  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK809">
<l>keṭāa vaḻivanta kēṇmaiyār kēṇmai</l>
<l>viṭāar viḻaiyu mulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They will be loved by the world, who have not forsaken the friendship of those with whom they have kept up an unbroken long-standing intimacy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
